dcterms:description: This dataset contains 30 Abdominal CT volumes with segmentation of 13 structures: the spleen, the left/right kidney, the gallbladder, the esophagus, the liver, the stomach, the aorta, the inferior vena cava, the portal and splenic veins, the pancreas, and the left/right adrenal gland.
